==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Creepingly
<hw>Creep"ing*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>by creeping slowly; in the
manner of a reptile; insidiously; cunningly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How slily and <qex>creepingly</qex> did he address himself to our
first parents.</q> <rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Creeple</ent>⟦br⟧
